{"tid":2312193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益］律師手足一齊嚟分析吓黎智英嘅罪行","createTime":"2020-12-04T16:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T17:55:22.000Z","uid":127052,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"852045b8c37e24bb7ca85ea2d8d077849b8b9d02","tid":2312193,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-55169222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-55169222&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=b3ed775d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-55169222&h=8f5006f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-55169222</a><br />\n起訴文件指出，涉案土地是蘋果日報印刷有限公司自1995年起向科技園公司前身香港工業邨公司租用，被告人沒有在租賃契約所容許下使用該處所部分地方，並意圖誘使科技園公司不作為，導致蘋果印刷或力高公司獲利，或導致科技園公司蒙受不利。<br />\n <br />\n點解係刑事罪行？<br />\n當硬夾嚟屈到係刑事，單就呢項控罪，有乜理據拒絕保釋？<br />\n你話謀殺罪，販毒，都話有潛逃或者其他風險<br />\n冇申報Subletting賺咗少少錢，有乜理由唔批準保釋要囚禁？<br />\n<br />\n如果蘋果係違反合約咁分租而謀利<br />\n當真有其事 頂多都係賠返科技園嘅損失<br />\n既然係土地事宜，應該係民事途徑解決<br />\n大不了咪收返塊地同賠償科技園嘅租金損失<br />\n<br />\n香港司法制度係唔係玩撚完？<br />\n利申：唔係做開Corporate Crime，有錯請指教"},{"pid":"8364de38267321983b8d1ff6b20ca9e6cba93667","tid":2312193,"uid":222692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db75bc85242a462036e5fe72cf4e5728bbe59525","tid":2312193,"uid":44209,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/tra